

	 
      For it is not you who speak, but the Spirit of your Father who speaks in you. --Matthew 10:20  One of my life verses :-) God showed it to me years back when I wasn't sure what to say when witnessing to others...how to approach them without frightening them off. As I grow older, and a little bit wiser, I realize how powerful this verse is...I don't know where I'd be without it today.
     

    
